  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 44ff468522a88594f835ce1750834844, type: 3}
  m_Name: Combat2Intro
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  dialogue:
  - A good pilot should be prepared for anything.
  - Even an armed ambush should not phase you.
  - Take both of these bots out.
  - When multiple targets are in attack range, you can cycle between them with 'Q'
    and 'E'.
  - Be careful, if either of these enemies are alive on their turns, they will attack
    you.
  - You may want to prioritize one target over spreading attacks out to reduce the
    damage you take.
